text: Rolando Zanni (born 8 February 1914, date of death unknown) was an Italian alpine skier. He competed in the men's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Italy Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:People from the Province of Pistoia
